<ul class="bac">	
	<li>Excellent degree/PhD in a mathematical or financial discipline </li>	
	<li>Excellent communication skills </li>	
	<li>Strong problem solving and analytical skills </li>	
	<li>Strong quantitative background </li>	
	<li>Ability to think creatively </li>	
	<li>Familiarity with programming </li>
</ul>

